strapiEvent.name: Little Sprouts Pop-Up: Valentine’s Day
strapiEvent.location: Botanical Garden of the Ozarks - Fayetteville, AR
strapiEvent.description:
Come get crafty and kind as we learn how to love ourselves and others during this Little Sprouts Pop-Up for Valentine’s Day.

First, we will have songs, story-time, and crafts inside. Then, a brisk walk in the Garden to find the first blooms of the year!

FREE/members or price of admission/nonmembers
